The experimental set-up used was equipped with a low-pressure radiofrequency (13.56 MHz) Electron Cyclotron Wave Resonance Plasma Enhanced Chemical Vapour (ECWR-PECVD) source (COPRA DN 200 CF, CCR Technology)13. This specific plasma source consists in a single turn RF driven electrode and a low transverse static magnetic field (B→\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
